r registration drives at music festivals because they know youth are much less likely to bother going to the polls on election day, so they can use the registrations for fake votes.</p>\n<p>How likely do you think it is a fentanyl addict on skid row would go to a voting booth or fill out a mail in ballot?</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 8, "score_up": 134, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASsnHqFk0", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 74, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8667250, "raw_content": "", "author": "wst4", "created": 1780926413532, "profile_picture": "K15ahGsDhQtO", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "journalist", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "media.scored.co", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASsnHqFk0.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://media.scored.co/post/BBnz8844q8Jc.jpeg", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [{"reference": "/scale/VYH8R5QaxkVwEnnX.jpeg", "width": 679, "content-type": "jpeg", "height": 428}], "blurhash": "UIJZYv0N?G%f%M}pOrM}NH57%1ni-:0gr?-:", "full_resolution": [428, 679]}, "title": "True", "last_comment_created": 1780936707537, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": true, "comments": 2, "score_up": 74, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "2063606719541108766",